ysis engine and adaptive challenges to keep automated software from engaging in abusive activities on your site. '=>'Gravity Forms 能與  reCAPTCHA 整合。reCAPTCHA 是一項免費的 CAPTCHA 服務，使用進階的風險分析引擎和適應性挑戰問題，以防止自動化軟件濫用你網站上的功能。','reCAPTCHA Settings'=>'reCAPTCHA 設定','Settings: General'=>'設定：一般','Enable Akismet Integration'=>'啟用 Akismet 整合','Enable to prevent extraneous scripts and styles from being printed on a Gravity Forms admin pages, reducing conflicts with other plugins and themes.'=>'啟用此功能可防止在 Gravity Forms 的管理頁面中輸出多餘的 &lt;scipt&gt; 和樣式，從而減少與其他外掛和佈景主題的衝突。','No Conflict Mode'=>'無衝突模式','Enable Automatic Background Updates'=>'啟用背景自動更新','Enable to allow Gravity Forms to download and install bug fixes and security updates automatically in the background. Requires a valid license key.'=>'啟用以允許 Gravity Forms 在背景自動下載並安裝錯誤修復程序和安全更新。此功能需要有效的序號。','Automatic Background Updates'=>'自動背景更新','Enable Toolbar Menu'=>'啟用工具欄選單','Enable to display the forms menu in the WordPress top toolbar. The forms menu will display the ten forms recently opened in the form editor.'=>'啟用此功能會在 WordPress 頂部的工具欄中顯示「表格」選單。表格選單將顯示最近在表格編輯器中打開過的十份表格。','Enable Logging'=>'啟用系統日誌','Enable if you would like logging within Gravity Forms. Logging allows you to easily debug the inner workings of Gravity Forms to solve any possible issues. '=>'系統日誌能讓你了解 Gravity Forms 的內部運作，有助找出發生問題的部份並加以解決。','Logging'=>'系統日誌','Select the default currency for your forms. This is used for product fields, credit card fields and others.'=>'設定預設貨幣。此選項適用於商品和信用卡欄位等。','Default Currency'=>'預設貨幣','Disable CSS'=>'停用 CSS','Output Default CSS'=>'輸出預設 CSS','Paste Your License Key Here'=>'貼上序號','A valid license key is required for access to automatic plugin upgrades and product support.'=>'持有有效的序號方可取得自動更新和技術支援。','Support License Key'=>'支援序號','Warning! ALL Gravity Forms data, including form entries will be deleted. This cannot be undone. \'OK\' to delete, \'Cancel\' to stop'=>'警告！所有 Gravity Forms 設定將被刪除。此操作無法復原。按「確定」繼續，或按「取消」中止操作。 ','Gravity Forms has been successfully uninstalled. It can be re-activated from the %splugins page%s.'=>'已成功停用 Gravity Forms。你可在%s外掛%s頁面中重新啟用。','You don\'t have adequate permission to uninstall Gravity Forms.'=>'你沒有足夠的權限停用 Gravity Forms。','Select the visibility for this field.'=>'設定此欄位的顯示模式。','The field is only visible when administering submitted entries. The field is not visible or functional when viewing the form.'=>'只可在管理已提交的條目時可看見此欄位。查看表格時，用戶不會看到此欄位，而此欄位亦不會起任何作用。','Administrative'=>'僅限管理用','The field is hidden when viewing the form. Useful when you require the functionality of this field but do not want the user to be able to see this field.'=>'查看表格時，隱藏此欄位。適合在需要此欄位的功能，卻又不希望用戶看到此欄位時使用。','Default option. The field is visible when viewing the form.'=>'預設選項。查看表格時，可看見此欄位。','Visible'=>'可見','Cancel this upload'=>'取消上傳','Please wait for the uploading to complete'=>'上載中，請稍等','There was a problem while saving the file on the server'=>'在伺服器上保存檔案時出現問題','Maximum number of files reached'=>'已達檔案數目上限','This type of file is not allowed.'=>'不支援此類型的檔案。','File exceeds size limit'=>'檔案超出大小限制','in progress'=>'處理中','Delete this file'=>'刪除檔案','This type of file is not allowed. Must be one of the following: '=>'不支援此類型的檔案。請使用下列檔案類型：','Voided'=>'無效','Refunded'=>'已退款','Cancelled'=>'已取消','Failed'=>'失敗','Processing'=>'處理中','Paid'=>'已付款','Authorized'=>'已授權','Transaction ID'=>'交易 ID','Source URL'=>'來源網址','Starred'=>'已加星號','Any form field'=>'任何欄位','Predefined Choices'=>'預設選項','Custom Choices'=>'自訂選項','Remove a condition'=>'移除條件','Add a condition'=>'添加條件','Please enter a confirmation name.'=>'請輸入確認訊息的名稱。','Please enter a URL.'=>'請輸入網址。','Please select a page.'=>'請選擇頁面。','Untitled Confirmation'=>'未命名確認訊息','There are unsaved changes to the current confirmation. Would you like to discard these changes?'=>'此確認訊息尚有未儲存的修訂。你是否要放棄這些修訂？','Are you sure you wish to delete this confirmation?'=>'你確定要刪除此確認訊息？','There was an issue saving this confirmation.'=>'儲存此確認訊息時出現問題。','Are you sure you wish to cancel these changes?'=>'你確定要放棄這些修訂？','Saving...'=>'儲存中⋯⋯','Send this notification if'=>'發送此通知書，但必須符合下列','Use this confirmation if'=>'使用此確認訊息，但必須符合下列','Empty (no choices selected)'=>'空白的（未有選取任何選項）','of the following match:'=>'條件：','Conditional LogicAny'=>'任何','Conditional LogicAll'=>'所有','Hide'=>'隱藏','Show'=>'顯示','this form button if'=>'本按鈕，但必須符合下列','this section if'=>'本節，但必須符合下列','this field if'=>'本欄位，但必須符合下列','We would love to hear from you! Please fill out this form and we will get in touch with you shortly.'=>'我們希望得到你的寶貴意見！請填寫此表格，我們會盡快與你聯絡。','Untitled Form'=>'未命名表格','Enter a value'=>'值','5 of %d items shown. Edit field to view all'=>'目前只顯示其中 5 個選項。編輯欄位以查看全部 %d 個選項','Select a format'=>'選擇格式','The form has been saved.  The content contains the link to return and complete the form.'=>'已儲存資料。內容中已包含返回本頁完成表格的鏈結。','Row removed'=>'已移除該行','New row added.'=>'已添加新行。','Pricing fields are not editable'=>'不可編輯商貿欄位','%1$s at %2$s'=>'%1$s %2$s','%s ago'=>'%s前','Gravity Forms requires WordPress %s or greater. You must upgrade WordPress in order to use Gravity Forms'=>'Gravity Forms 需要 WordPress %s 或更高的版本。你必須升級 WordPress 才能使用 Gravity Forms。','Cannot send email because the FROM address is invalid.'=>'寄件者地址無效，無法發送電郵。','Cannot send email because there is no SUBJECT and no MESSAGE.'=>'沒有主題及內文，無法發送電郵。','Cannot send email because the TO address is invalid.'=>'收件者地址無效，無法發送電郵。','Allowable form fields'=>'可使用的欄位','Full Size - Right Aligned'=>'完整大小—靠右對齊','Full Size - Centered'=>'完整大小—置中','Full Size - Left Aligned'=>'完整大小—靠左對齊','Full Size'=>'完整大小','Large - Right Aligned'=>'大—靠右對齊','Large - Centered'=>'大—置中','Large - Left Aligned'=>'大—靠左對齊','Medium - Right Aligned'=>'中—靠右對齊','Medium - Centered'=>'中—置中','Medium - Left Aligned'=>'中—靠左對齊','Thumbnail - Right Aligned'=>'縮圖—靠右對齊','Thumbnail - Centered'=>'縮圖—置中','Thumbnail - Left Aligned'=>'縮圖—靠左對齊','Thumbnail'=>'縮圖','Select image size'=>'選擇圖像尺寸','Pricing form fields'=>'商貿欄位','Optional form fields'=>'選填欄位','Required form fields'=>'必填欄位','Post Edit URL'=>'編輯文章的網址','Form Id'=>'表格 ID','Entry URL'=>'條目網址','All Pricing Fields'=>'所有商貿欄位','All Submitted Fields'=>'所有有提交資料的欄位','Select an action for this shortcode. Actions are added by some add-ons.'=>'部份外掛會添加指令，請選擇此 shortcode 要執行的指令。','Select an action'=>'選擇指令','Specify the starting tab index for the fields of this form.'=>'設定表格欄位的 tabindex 起始值。','Specify whether or not to use Ajax to submit the form.'=>'是否使用 AJAX 提交表格。','Whether or not to display the form description.'=>'是否顯示表格說明。','Whether or not to display the form title.'=>'是否顯示表格標題。','Can\'t find your form? Make sure it is active.'=>'找不到表格？請確保你已將其狀態設定為「使用中」。','Select a form from the list to add it to your post or page.'=>'選擇要添加到文章或頁面中的表格。','Select a form below to add it to your post or page.'=>'選擇要添加到文章或頁面中的表格。','All Forms'=>'所有表格','Recent'=>'最近','Preview this form'=>'預覽此表格','Editor'=>'編輯器','Oops! There was an error saving the form title. Please refresh the page and try again.'=>'糟糕！儲存表格標題時出錯。請重新整理頁面，然後重試。','The %sSend To%s email address provided is not valid.'=>'提供的%s寄件者%s電郵地址無效。','No notifications have been selected. Please select a notification to be sent.'=>'尚未選擇任何通知書。請選擇要發送的通知書。','There was an error while resending the notifications.'=>'重新發送通知書時出錯。','Add-On browser is currently unavailable. Please try again later.'=>'無法加載外掛一覽。請稍後再試。','Finished'=>'已完成','Unable to disable logging.'=>'無法停用系統日誌。','Logging disabled.'=>'已停用系統日誌。','Failed to load the preview for this form.'=>'無法加載此表格的預覽。','Please select a form.'=>'請選擇表格。','Dismiss'=>'關閉','There is an update available for Gravity Forms. %sView Details%s'=>'Gravity Forms 有可用的更新。%s查看詳情%s','You don\'t have any forms. Let\'s go %screate one %s!'=>'你尚未設置任何表格。立即%s新增表格%s！','View All Forms'=>'查看全部表格','View All Entries'=>'查看全部條目','Last Entry: %s'=>'最新提交的條目：%s','Unread'=>'未讀取','Oops!! Something went wrong. %sPlease try again or %scontact us%s.'=>'糟糕！系統發生錯誤。%s請再試一次或%s與我們聯絡%s。','The versions of the following add-ons you\'re running haven\'t been tested with Gravity Forms %s. Please update them or confirm compatibility before updating Gravity Forms, or you may experience issues:'=>'下列外掛的版本尚未針對 Gravity Forms %s 作相容性測試。請在更新 Gravity Forms 前更新它們，或確保它們與新版本相容，否則系統有可能出現問題。','IMPORTANT: As this is a major update, we strongly recommend creating a backup of your site before updating.'=>'小心！這是一項重大更新，我們強烈建議你在更新前為網站備份。','<a href="%1$s" class="update-link" aria-label="Update %2$s now">'=>'<a href="%1$s" class="update-link" aria-label="立即更新 %2$s">','There is a new version of %1$s available. %2$sView version %3$s details%4$s or %5$supdate now%6$s. '=>'%1$s 有新的版本。%2$s查看有關版本的%3$s詳細資料%4$s或%5$s立即更新%6$s。','<a class="thickbox open-plugin-details-modal" aria-label="View %1$s version %2$s details" href="%3$s">'=>'<a class="thickbox open-plugin-details-modal" aria-label="查看 %1$s 版本 %2$s 的詳細資料" href="%3$s">','There is a new version of %1$s available. %2$sView version %3$s details%4$s. '=>'%1$s 有新的版本。%2$s查看 %3$s 的詳細資料%4$s。','This version of the %1$s is not compatible with the version of Gravity Forms that is installed. Upgrade this add-on to version %2$s or greater to avoid compatibility issues and potential loss of data.'=>'此版本的 %1$s 與所安裝的 Gravity Forms 不相容。更新此外掛至 %2$s 或更高的版本以解決相容性問題和避免遺失數據。','Please select a form'=>'請選擇表格','Add Form'=>'新增表格','Add Gravity Form'=>'新增 Gravity Form','New Form'=>'新增表格','Update Available'=>'有可用的更新','Upload folder is not writable. Export and file upload features will not be functional.'=>'上載文件夾不可寫。你將無法使用匯出和上載檔案功能。','REST API Settings'=>'REST API 設定','Logging Settings'=>'系統日誌設定','Uninstall Gravity Forms'=>'停用 Gravity Forms','View System Status'=>'查看系統狀態','Manage Add-Ons'=>'管理外掛','Manage Updates'=>'管理更新','Edit Plugin Settings'=>'編輯外掛設定','View Plugin Settings'=>'查看外掛設定','Edit Entry Notes'=>'編輯條目備註','View Entry Notes'=>'查看條目備註','Delete Entries'=>'刪除條目','Edit Entries'=>'編輯條目','View Entries'=>'查看條目','Preview Forms'=>'預覽表格','Edit Forms'=>'編輯表格','Delete Forms'=>'刪除表格','Create Forms'=>'新增表格','Autocomplete Attribute'=>'自動完成屬性','Placeholders will not be submitted along with the form. Use Placeholders to give a hint at the expected value or format.'=>'提交表格時，系統會無視提示字眼。你可利用提示字眼引導用戶填寫恰當的值或使用指定的格式。','The Placeholder will not be submitted along with the form. Use the Placeholder to give a hint at the expected value or format.'=>'提交表格時，系統會無視提示字眼。你可利用提示字眼引導用戶填寫恰當的值或使用指定的格式。','If you would like to pre-populate the value of a field, enter it here.'=>'你可選擇填寫預設值。','Select the fields you\'d like to use in this Address Field and customize the Sub-Labels by entering new ones.'=>'設定要使用的子欄位，並自訂其子標籤。','Add Choices to this field. You can mark a choice as selected by default by using the radio buttons on the left.'=>'添加選項至此欄位。你可使用左側的按鈕選定預設選項。','Name Prefix Choices'=>'前綴選項','Select the fields you\'d like to use in this Name field and customize the Sub-Labels by entering new ones.'=>'設定要使用的子欄位，並自訂其子標籤。','Select a form field size from the available options. This will set the width of the field. Please note: if using a paragraph field, the size applies only to the height of the field.'=>'設定欄位的闊度。注意：如你正使用多行文字欄位，此設定只會調整欄位的高度。','Select the sub-label placement.  Sub-labels can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs.'=>'選擇子標籤的擺放位置。子標籤可放在欄位的上方或下方。','Select the description placement.  Descriptions can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs.'=>'設定欄位說明的擺放位置。欄位說明可擺放在欄位的上方或下方。','Select the label visibility for this field.  Labels can either inherit the form setting or be hidden.'=>'選擇欄位標籤的顯示模式。欄位標籤可繼承表格的全局設置，或在此設定為「隱藏」。','Label Visibility'=>'標籤顯示模式','Enter values in this setting to override the Sub-Label for each field.'=>'填寫資料以覆蓋此欄位中的子標籤。','Enter the admin label of the form field.  Entering a value in this field will override the Field Label when displayed in the Gravity Forms administration tool.'=>'設定此欄位的管理用標籤。此欄填寫的資料會覆蓋顯示在 Gravity Forms 管理工具中的欄位標籤。','Admin Label'=>'管理用標籤','Specify how many decimal places the number should be rounded to.'=>'設定要保留小數點後的多少個位。','Specify a mathematical formula. The result of this formula will be dynamically populated as the value for this field.'=>'設定數學公式。公式的運算結果會自動成為此欄位的值。','Enabling calculations will allow the value of this field to be dynamically calculated based on a mathematical formula.'=>'啟用算式功能會讓此欄位的值以數學公式動態計算。','Enter the minimum and maximum values for this form field.  This will require that the value entered by the user must fall within this range.'=>'設定此欄位的數值上限和下限。用戶輸入的值必須在此範圍內。','Number Range'=>'數目範圍','Select this option to hide the field label in the form.'=>'勾選以隱藏表格中的欄位標籤。','Hide Field Label'=>'隱藏欄位標籤','Select this option to limit user input to unique values only.  This will require that a value entered in a field does not currently exist in the entry database for that field.'=>'令用戶只能輸入獨一無二的值。用戶在此欄填寫的資料不可與資料庫已有的記錄相同。','Select this option to make the form field required.  A required field will prevent the form from being submitted if it is not filled out or selected.'=>'將表格欄位設定成必填欄位。如未有填寫或選取任何選項，則無法提交表格。','Required Field'=>'必填欄位','Enter the description for the form field.  This will be displayed to the user and provide some direction on how the field should be filled out or selected.'=>'輸入表格欄位說明。欄位說明可引導用戶如何填寫欄位或選取選項。','Field Description'=>'欄位說明','Select the format you would like to use for the phone input.  Available options are domestic US/CANADA style phone number and international long format phone number.'=>'選擇電話號碼的格式。你可選擇使用美加或國際通用的電話號碼格式。','Phone Number Format'=>'電話號碼格式','Specify the maximum file size in megabytes allowed for each of the files.'=>'設定每個檔案的大小上限（以MB為單位）。','Specify the maximum number of files that can be uploaded using this field. Leave blank for unlimited. Note that the actual number of files permitted may be limited by this server\'s specifications and configuration.'=>'設定使用此欄位上傳檔案時的上限。如無須限制數量，則將此欄留空。請注意，實際數量有可能受伺服器的規格和配置所限。','Select this option to enable multiple files to be uploaded for this field.'=>'勾選此框，讓用戶可透過此欄位上載多個檔案。','Enter the allowed file extensions for file uploads.  This will limit the type of files a user may upload.'=>'輸入允許的檔案副檔名。這會限制用戶可以上傳的檔案類型。','Allowed File Extensions'=>'允許的檔案副檔名','Select the format you would like to use for the time field.  Available options are 12 hour (i.e. 8:30 pm) and 24 hour (i.e. 20:30).'=>'選擇時間欄位的格式。你可選擇 12小時制（即 8:30 PM）或 24小時制（即 20:30）。','Select the format you would like to use for the date input.'=>'選擇日期欄位的格式。','Field Date Format'=>'日期格式','Check this box to prevent this field from being displayed in a non-secure page (i.e. not https://). It will redirect the page to the same URL, but starting with https:// instead. This option requires a properly configured SSL certificate.'=>'如要避免表格在非安全頁面中顯示（即不是以 https:// 開頭的頁面），請勾選此框。啟用時，系統會將頁面重新導向至相同的網址，但相關頁面會以 https:// 開頭。使用此選項時，請確保你已正確配置 SSL 證書。','Select the format of numbers that are allowed in this field. You have the option to use a comma or a dot as the decimal separator.'=>'選擇此欄位所允許的數字格式。你可選擇使用逗號或一點作為小數分隔符號。','Select the format you would like to use for the Name field.  There are 3 options, Normal which includes First and Last Name, Extended which adds Prefix and Suffix, or Simple which is a single input field.'=>'選擇名稱欄位的格式。共有三個選項：一般（包括姓氏和名字）、擴充（包括前綴和後綴）或簡單（即單一欄位）。','Field Name Format'=>'名稱格式','Check this box to prevent the State/Province/Region from being displayed in the form.'=>'如無需顯示州份／省份／地區欄位，請勾選此框。','Hide State/Province/Region'=>'隱藏州份／省份／地區','Check this box to prevent Province field from being displayed in the form.'=>'如無需顯示省份，請勾選此框。','Hide Province Field'=>'隱藏省份欄位','Check this box to prevent the State field from being displayed in the form.'=>'如無需顯示州份，請勾選此框。','Hide State Field'=>'隱藏州份欄位','Check this box to prevent the extra address input (Address Line 2) from being displayed in the form.'=>'如無需顯示額外的地址欄位（地址行 2），請勾選此框。','Hide Address Line 2'=>'隱藏地址行 2','For addresses that only apply to one country, you can choose to not display the country drop down. Entries will still be recorded with the selected country.'=>'如地址格式只適用於某特定國家／地區，你可選擇不顯示國家／地區下拉選單。在提交條目時，系統依然會記錄所選的國家／地區。','Hide Country'=>'隱藏國家／地區','Select the country you would like to be selected by default when the form gets displayed.'=>'選擇在顯示表格時預先選定的國家／地區。','Select the province you would like to be selected by default when the form gets displayed.'=>'選擇在顯示表格時預先選定的省份。','Default Province'=>'預設省份','Select the state you would like to be selected by default when the form gets displayed.'=>'選擇在顯示表格時預先選定的州份。','Default State'=>'預設州份','Select the type of address you would like to use.'=>'選擇地址格式。','Select the type of inputs you would like to use for the date field. Date Picker will let users select a date from a calendar. Date Field will let users free type the date.'=>'選擇日期欄位的輸入模式。互動式日曆會讓用戶使用一個模仿實物的介面中選擇日期。年月日欄位會讓用戶自行輸入日期。','Enter the maximum number of rows that users are allowed to add.'=>'輸入用戶可添加的列數上限。','Enter the maximum number of characters that this field is allowed to have.'=>'設定此欄位的字符上限。','Select the type of field from the available form fields.'=>'選擇欄位類型。','Field type'=>'欄位類型','Select the custom field name from available existing custom fields, or enter a new custom field name.'=>'選擇現有的自訂欄位，或輸入新的自訂欄位名稱。','Select the position of the badge containing the links to Google\'s privacy policy and terms.'=>'選擇商標的擺放位置。此商標包含 Google 私隱權政策和條款的鏈結。','CAPTCHA Badge Position'=>'CAPTCHA 商標擺放位置','Select the type of CAPTCHA you would like to use.'=>'選擇你要使用的CAPTCHA類型。','CAPTCHA Type'=>'CAPTCHA 類型','Select the visual theme for the reCAPTCHA field from the available options to better match your site design.'=>'選擇 reCAPTCHA 欄位的外觀主題以配合網站的設計。','reCAPTCHA Theme'=>'reCAPTCHA 主題','When enabled, margins are added to properly align the HTML content with other form fields.'=>'啟用時會添加邊距，使 HTML 內容與其他的表格欄位對齊。','Disable Default Margins'=>'移除預設邊距','Enter the label for this HTML block. It will help you identify your HTML blocks in the form editor, but it will not be displayed on the form.'=>'輸入此 HTML 區塊的標籤。此標籤不會在表格上顯示，但有助你在表格編輯器中辨識對應的 HTML 區塊。','Enter the label of the form field.  This is the field title the user will see when filling out the form.'=>'請輸入欄位標籤。用戶在填寫表格時會看到此欄位標題。','To pass field data to the confirmation page, build a Query String using the \'Insert Merge Tag\' drop down. %s..more info on querystrings &raquo;%s'=>'要將欄位資料傳送到確認頁面，請使用「插入智能標籤」下拉選單，構建網址參數。%s了解更有關網址參數的資訊%s','Pass Data Via Query String'=>'通過網址參數載入欄位的值','Enter the URL of the webpage you would like the user to be redirected to after they have submitted the form.'=>'設定用戶提交表格後重新導向至的網址。','Redirect Form to URL'=>'將表格重新導向到網址','Select the page you would like the user to be redirected to after they have submitted the form.'=>'設定用戶提交表格後重新導向至的頁面。','Redirect Form to Page'=>'將表格重新導向到頁面','When enabled, auto-formatting will insert paragraph breaks automatically. Disable auto-formatting when using HTML to create the confirmation content.'=>'在啟用的情況下，系統會自動在適當的地方插入分段符號。如要使用 HTML 撰寫確認訊息，請停用自動格式化。','Enter the text you would like the user to see on the confirmation page of this form.'=>'輸入用戶在確認頁面上看到的文字。','Confirmation Message Text'=>'文本確認訊息','Enter the URL of a custom image to replace the default \'delete item\' icon. A maximum size of 16px by 16px is recommended'=>'輸入用以取代預設的「刪除此列」圖示網址。建議的最大尺寸為16px ⨉ 16px','Enter the URL of a custom image to replace the default \'add item\' icon. A maximum size of 16px by 16px is recommended'=>'輸入用以取代預設的「添加新列」圖示網址。建議的最大尺寸為16px ⨉ 16px','Enter the CSS class name you would like to use in order to override the default styles for this form.'=>'輸入你希望使用的 CSS Class 以覆蓋此表格的預設樣式。','Form CSS Class Name'=>'表格 CSS Class','Enter the path to an image you would like to use as the form submit button.'=>'設定用作提交表格的按鈕的圖片路徑。','Form Button Image'=>'表格按鈕圖片','Enter the text you would like to appear on the form submit button.'=>'設定提交表格的按鈕上的文字。','Form Button Text'=>'表格按鈕文字','Required Indicator'=>'必填指標','Select the default sub-label placement.  Sub-labels can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs. This setting can be overridden in the appearance settings for each field.'=>'選擇預設的子標籤擺放位置。子標籤可放在欄位的上方或下方，亦可在每個欄位的外觀設定中覆蓋此設定。','Select the default description placement.  Descriptions can be placed above the field inputs or below the field inputs. This setting can be overridden in the appearance settings for each field.'=>'選擇預設的說明文字擺放位置。說明文字可放在欄位的上方或下方，亦可在每個欄位的外觀設定中覆蓋此設定。','Select the default label placement.  Labels can be top aligned above a field, left aligned to the left of a field, or right aligned to the right of a field. This is a global label placement setting.'=>'選擇預設的標籤擺放位置。標籤可擺放在欄位以上並靠上對齊、欄位的左側並靠左對齊，或欄位的右側並靠右對齊。','Form Label Placement'=>'表格標籤擺放位置','Enter a description for your form. This may be used for user instructions.'=>'輸入表格說明。此說明可用作填表指引。','Enter the title of your form.'=>'輸入表格標題。','Check this option to enable Gravity Forms\' legacy markup. This will hinder the accessibility of your form.'=>'勾選此選項以使用 Gravity Forms 的舊版源碼。使用舊版源碼會對無障礙使用體驗帶來負面影響。','Legacy Markup'=>'舊版源碼','Check this option to enable a sliding animation when displaying/hiding conditional logic fields.'=>'勾選此選項，在顯示或隱藏條件邏輯欄位時加入滑動效果。','Enable Animation'=>'啟用動畫','Enables the honeypot spam protection technique, which is an alternative to the reCAPTCHA field.'=>'以誘捕系統作防護，可作為 reCAPTCHA 的替代方案。','Enable Anti-spam honeypot'=>'啟用反垃圾訊息誘捕系統','Schedule a time period the form is active.'=>'安排表格變成現行狀態的時間。','Enter a number in the input box below to limit the number of entries allowed for this form. The form will become inactive when that number is reached.'=>'在下面的輸入框中輸入數字以限制此表格允許的輸入數量。到違該數字後，表格會變為非現行狀態。','Limit Number of Entries'=>'限制條目數量','Limit the number of entries a form can generate and/or schedule a time period the form is active.'=>'限制表格

條目數量
及／或

安排表格變成現行狀態的時段。','Limit Form Activity'=>'限制表格活動','When enabled, any files uploaded to File Upload fields will be attached to the notification email.'=>'啟用時，任何經「上載檔案」欄位添加的檔案都會加到電郵通知書中。','Enter a comma separated list of email addresses you would like to receive a BCC of the notification email.'=>'輸入應以密件副本形式收取電郵通知書的電郵地址。如收件者多於一個，請以逗號分隔。','Blind Carbon Copy Addresses'=>'密件副本地址','Enter a comma separated list of email addresses you would like to receive a CC of the notification email.'=>'輸入應以副本抄送形式收取電郵通知書的電郵地址。如收件者多於一個，請以逗號分隔。','Carbon Copy Addresses'=>'副本地址','Enter the email address you would like to be used as the reply to address for the notification email.'=>'輸入在電郵通知書中用作「回覆至」的電郵地址。','Enter the name you would like the notification email sent from, or select the name from available name fields.'=>'輸入寄件者名稱或選擇適當的名稱欄位以插入智能標籤。','Enter an authorized email address you would like the notification email sent from. To avoid deliverability issues, always use your site domain in the from email.'=>'輸入已獲授權的寄件者電郵地址。為免發生問題，寄件者電郵地址的域名應與網站的域名相同。','From Email Address'=>'寄件者電郵地址','Allows notification to be sent to different email addresses depending on values selected in the form.'=>'按表格中特定欄位的值，將通知書發送到不同的電郵地址。','Routing'=>'條件導向','When enabled, auto-formatting will insert paragraph breaks automatically. Disable auto-formatting when using HTML to create email notification content.'=>'在啟用的情況下，系統會自動在適當的地方插入分段符號。如要使用 HTML 撰寫電郵通知書，請停用自動格式化。','Disable Auto-Formatting'=>'停用自動格式化','Enter the email address you would like the notification email sent to.'=>'輸入電郵通知書的收件者電郵地址。','Send To Email Address'=>'發送至電郵','New submission from'=>'新條目：','User Login'=>'用戶帳號','User Email'=>'用戶電郵','User Display Name'=>'用戶顯示名稱','HTTP Referer URL'=>'HTTP Referer URL','HTTP User Agent'=>'HTTP User Agent','Embed Post/Page Title'=>'嵌入表格的文章／頁面標題','Embed Post/Page Id'=>'嵌入表格的文章／頁面 ID','User IP Address'=>'用戶 IP 地址','Insert Merge Tag'=>'插入智能標籤','Pricing Fields'=>'商貿欄位','Post Fields'=>'文章欄位','View Form'=>'查看表格','Form Updated'=>'已更