tion has been fulfilled, if applicable.'=>'交易是否已完成（如適用）。','The transaction ID for the payment, if applicable.'=>'交易 ID（如適用）。','The payment method for the payment, if applicable.'=>'付款方式（如適用）。','The amount of the payment, if applicable.'=>'交易金額（如適用）。','The date of the payment, if applicable.'=>'交易日期（如適用）。','The status of the payment, if applicable.'=>'交易狀態（如適用）。','The user agent string for the browser used to submit the entry.'=>'提交條目時所用的瀏覽器的 User Agent。','The URL where the form was embedded.'=>'嵌入表格的頁面網址。','The IP address of the entry creator.'=>'提交者的 IP 地址。','Whether the entry has been read.'=>'條目是否已讀取。','Whether the entry is starred.'=>'條目是否已加星號。','The date the entry was updated, in UTC.'=>'條目更新的日期（以 UTC 格式顯示）。','The date the entry was created, in UTC.'=>'條目生成的日期（以 UTC 格式顯示）。','The Form ID for the entry.'=>'條目所屬的表格 ID。','Unique identifier for the resource.'=>'資源的唯一標識符。','Missing entry JSON'=>'欠條目 JSON','The field values.'=>'欄位值。','The input values.'=>'輸入值。','Form not found.'=>'找不到表格。','The Form object must be sent as a JSON string in the request body with the content-type header set to application/json.'=>'表格物件（object）必須在請求內容中以JSON 字符串發送，其內容類型標頭設置為application / json。','The form has already been deleted.'=>'該表格已被刪除。','Invalid form id.'=>'表格 ID 無效。','The add-on the feed belongs to.'=>'訊息流所屬的外掛。','The JSON string containing the feed meta.'=>'包含訊息流中繼資料的 JSON 字符串。','The Form ID for the feed.'=>'訊息流所屬的表格 ID。','Unique identifier for the feed.'=>'feed的唯一標識符。','Missing feed meta'=>'欠訊息流中繼資料','Missing add-on slug'=>'欠外掛的 slug','Missing feed JSON'=>'欠訊息流 JSON','Missing Key Value Pairs JSON'=>'遺失 Key Value Pairs JSON','Entry updated successfully'=>'已成功更新條目。','Property values should be sent as an array'=>'屬性值應為關聯陣列','No property values were found in the request body'=>'在請求的內容中找不到屬性值。','You don\'t have any API keys. Let\'s go %1$screate one%2$s!'=>'你尚未設置任何 API Key。立即%1$s新增 API Key%2$s！','Never Accessed'=>'從未使用','Last Access'=>'最後使用日期','Permissions'=>'權限','User'=>'用戶','Create A Form'=>'新增表格','Installation Complete'=>'安裝完成','Congratulations! Click the \'Create A Form\' button to get started.'=>'恭喜！你已成功安裝，按「新增表格」開始使用。','Global Settings'=>'全局設置','Protect your form entries from spam using Akismet.'=>'使用 Akismet 保護你的表格免受垃圾訊息影響。','Akismet Integration'=>'Akismet 整合','Set this to ON to display the Forms menu in the WordPress top toolbar. The Forms menu will display the latest ten forms recently opened in the form editor.'=>'啟用此功能會在 WordPress 頂部的工具欄中顯示「表格」選單。表格選單將顯示最近在表格編輯器中打開過的十份表格。','Toolbar Menu'=>'工具欄選單','Set this to ON to prevent extraneous scripts and styles from being printed on Gravity Forms admin pages, reducing conflicts with other plugins and themes.'=>'啟用此功能可防止在 Gravity Forms 的管理頁面中輸出多餘的 &lt;scipt&gt; 和樣式，從而減少與其他外掛和佈景主題的衝突。','Off'=>'停用','On'=>'啟用','Select a Currency'=>'選擇貨幣','Back'=>'返回','Next'=>'下一頁','Please accept the terms'=>'請接受有關條款。','Invalid or Expired Key : Please make sure you have entered the correct value and that your key is not expired.'=>'序號無效或已過期：請確保你輸入的序號正確而且仍未過期。','Please enter a valid license key.'=>'請輸入有效的序號。','License Key'=>'序號','I understand the risks of not providing a valid license key.'=>'我了解不提供有效序號的風險。','If you don\'t enter a valid license key, you will not be able to update Gravity Forms when important bug fixes and security enhancements are released. This can be a serious security risk for your site.'=>'如你不輸入有效的序號，你將無法更新 Gravity Forms 以修復程式漏洞和強化系統安全。這有可能為你的網站帶來嚴重的安全風險。','Enter your Gravity Forms License Key below.  Your key unlocks access to automatic updates, the add-on installer, and support.  You can find your key on the My Account page on the %sGravity Forms%s site.'=>'請輸入你的 Gravity Forms 序號。序號能讓你啟用自動更新、安裝外掛和取得技術支援。你可在 %sGravity Forms%s 網站上的「我的帳戶」頁面上找到有關序號。','Disabled'=>'已停用','Please accept the terms.'=>'請接受上列條款。','Background Updates'=>'背景更新','I understand and accept the risk of not enabling background updates.'=>'我了解並接受停用背景自動更新所帶來的風險。','By disabling background updates your site may not get critical bug fixes and security enhancements. We only recommend doing this if you are experienced at managing a WordPress site and accept the risks involved in manually keeping your WordPress site updated.'=>'停用此功能有可能使你的網站無法獲得極為重要的更新以修復程式漏洞及強化系統安全。除非你有管理 WordPress 網站的經驗及願意承擔有關風險，否則你不應停用自動更新。','Are you sure?'=>'你確定？','Turn off background updates'=>'關閉背景更新','Keep background updates enabled'=>'啟用背景更新','Updates will only be available if you have entered a valid License Key'=>'網站只會在你輸入有效的序號後才收到更新','This feature is activated by default unless you opt to disable it below. We only recommend disabling background updates if you intend on managing updates manually.'=>'除非你主動調整，否則此功能會預設為「使用中」。只有在你打算手動管理更新時，我們才建議你將此功能停用。','Gravity Forms will download important bug fixes, security enhancements and plugin updates automatically. Updates are extremely important to the security of your WordPress site.'=>'Gravity Forms 將自動下載重要的更新，以修復程式漏洞、強化系統安全及補充外掛資源。這些更新對你的網站安全極為重要。','Welcome to Gravity Forms'=>'歡迎使用 Gravity Forms','There was a problem while inserting the field values'=>'儲存表格欄位的資料時出現問題','There was a problem while inserting one of the input values for the entry'=>'儲存表格欄位輸入框的資料時出現問題','An error prevented the entry for this form submission being saved. Please contact support.'=>'系統出錯，無法儲存提交的資料。請聯絡技術支援人員。','You don\'t have adequate permission to edit entries.'=>'你沒有足夠的權限修改條目。','Every %d Minutes'=>'每 %d 分鐘','Inactive'=>'閒置中','Active'=>'使用中','feeds'=>'訊息流','feed'=>'訊息流','Checkbox'=>'選框','Select which actions should only occur after payment has been received.'=>'選擇只在交易成功後才執行的指示。','Post Payment Actions'=>'交易後指示','Process %s feed only when payment is received.'=>'只在交易成功後才處理 %s 訊息流。','Invalid value'=>'數值無效','To get started, please configure your %s.'=>'請先設定 %s。','You don\'t have any feeds configured. Let\'s go %screate one%s!'=>'你尚未設置任何訊息流。立即%s新增訊息流%s！','\'Cancel\' to stop, \'OK\' to delete.'=>'按「取消」中止操作，或按「確定」繼續。','WARNING: You are about to delete this item.'=>'警告：你將刪除此項目。','Duplicate'=>'複製','Edit'=>'編輯','Delete'=>'刪除','There was an error updating this feed. Please review all errors below and try again.'=>'更新此訊息流時出錯。請檢查下列錯誤，然後重試。','Feed updated successfully.'=>'已成功更新訊息流。','You don\'t have sufficient permissions to update the form settings.'=>'你沒有足夠的權限更新表格設定。','Feed Settings'=>'訊息流設定','Unable to render feed settings.'=>'無法呈現訊息流設定。','%s Feeds'=>'%s 訊息流','Add New'=>'新增','Copy %d'=>'副本 %d','Copy 1'=>'副本 1','You don\'t have adequate permission to uninstall this add-on: '=>'你沒有足夠的權限停用此外掛：','Warning! ALL %s settings will be deleted. This cannot be undone. \'OK\' to delete, \'Cancel\' to stop'=>'警告！所有 %s 的設定將被刪除。此操作無法復原。按「確定」繼續，或按「取消」中止操作。','%sThis operation deletes ALL %s settings%s. If you continue, you will NOT be able to retrieve these settings.'=>'%s此操作將刪除所有 %s 的設定%s。你將無法復原這些設定。','Uninstall Add-On'=>'停用外掛','Uninstall %s Add-On'=>'停用外掛 %s','You don\'t have sufficient permissions to update the settings.'=>'你沒有足夠的權限更新設定。','Warning'=>'警告','Uninstall %s'=>'停用「%s」','%s has been successfully uninstalled. It can be re-activated from the %splugins page%s.'=>'已成功停用「%s」。你可在%s外掛%s頁面中重新啟用。','This add-on needs to be updated. Please contact the developer.'=>'此外掛需要更新，請聯絡開發人員。','You don\'t have adequate permission to view this page'=>'你沒有足夠的權限查看此頁。','Unable to render form settings.'=>'無法呈現表格設定。','Validation Error'=>'驗證錯誤','Add Custom Key'=>'新增自訂欄位名稱','Please add a %s field to your form.'=>'請添加「%s」欄位至表格中。','%s settings updated.'=>'已更新 %s 設定。','Field type \'%s\' has not been implemented'=>'尚未套用欄位類型「%s」。','Field could not be rendered.'=>'無法呈現欄位。','%s Settings'=>'%s 設定','Gravity Forms Add-Ons'=>'Gravity Forms 外掛','Results Page'=>'報告頁面','Add-On Settings'=>'外掛設定','Add-On Page'=>'外掛頁面','Uninstall'=>'停用','GF Add-Ons'=>'GF 外掛','Please resolve the following issues to use %s:'=>'請先解決以下問題以使用 %s：','%s is not able to run because your WordPress environment has not met the minimum requirements.'=>'由於 WordPress 環境未達最低要求，%s 無法運行。','Current WordPress version (%s) does not meet minimum WordPress version requirement (%s).'=>'目前的 WordPress 版本（%s）不符合版本最低要求（%s）。','Required PHP function missing: %s'=>'找不到所需的 PHP 函數：%s。','Required PHP extension "%s" does not meet minimum version requirement: %s.'=>'所需的 PHP 擴展套件「%s」不符合版本最低要求：%s。','Required PHP extension missing: %s'=>'找不到所需的 PHP 擴展套件：%s。','Current PHP version (%s) does not meet minimum PHP version requirement (%s).'=>'目前的 PHP 版本（%s）不符合版本最低要求（%s）。','Required WordPress plugin is missing: %s.'=>'找不到所需的 WordPress 插件：%s。','Required Gravity Forms Add-On "%s" does not meet minimum version requirement: %s.'=>'Gravity Forms 的外掛「%s」不符合版本最低要求：%s。','Required Gravity Forms Add-On is missing: %s.'=>'找不到所需的 Gravity Forms 外掛：%s。','Show more'=>'顯示更多','Latest values:'=>'最新的值：','Item'=>'項目','Average score'=>'平均分','Average global score'=>'總平均分','Frequency'=>'頻率','Choice'=>'選項','No entries for this field'=>'此欄位沒有任何資料','No results'=>'找不到相關結果','Entries processed: %1$d of %2$d'=>'已處理條目：%1$d 之 %2$d','There was an error while processing the entries. Please contact support.'=>'處理條目時出錯，請聯絡技術支援人員。','No results.'=>'找不到相關結果。','The average (mean) score: The sum of the scores divided by the number of entries.'=>'平均分：將欄位的總分除以條目總數。','Average Score'=>'平均分','The average (mean) score for the whole field. The sum of the total scores divided by the number of entries.'=>'總平均分：將欄位的總分除以條目總數。','Average Global Score'=>'總平均分','The average (mean) score for each row: the sum of all the scores for each row divided by the total number of entries.'=>'平均分（列）：以列為單位，將該列的總分除以條目總數。','Average Row Score'=>'平均分（列）','Narrow the results by adding filters. Note that some field types support more options than others.'=>'添加篩選條件以縮小結果範圍。注意：個別欄位類型會較其他有更多的選項。','Date Range is optional, if no date range is specified it will be ignored.'=>'日期範圍為選填項目。如沒有選擇日期範圍，系統會自動無視此篩選條件。','The aggregate rank is the overall rank for all entries based on the weighted scores for each item.'=>'總排名：將每一項目的加權總分由高至低排序而成。','Aggregate Rank'=>'總排名','Scores are weighted calculations. Items ranked higher are given a greater score than items that are ranked lower. The total score for each item is the sum of the weighted scores.'=>'分數以加權方式計算；權值越高，分數越高。總分所計算的是所有加權值的總和。','Total Score'=>'總分','This form does not have any fields that can be used for results'=>'此表格沒有任何適用於報告運算的欄位','Clear'=>'清除','Apply filters'=>'套用','End'=>'結束','Start'=>'開始','Date Range'=>'日期範圍','Filters'=>'篩選','Results'=>'報告','View results generated by this form'=>'查看此表格的報告','Error retrieving results. If the problem persists, please contact support.'=>'查找資料時出錯。如問題持續，請聯絡技術支援人員。','Results Filters'=>'篩選結果','Go to the last page'=>'前往最後一頁','Go to the next page'=>'前往下一頁','paging%1$s of %2$s'=>'%1$s 之 %2$s','Go to the previous page'=>'前往上一頁','Go to the first page'=>'前往第一頁','There hasn\'t been any sales in the specified date range.'=>'在指定的日期範圍內沒有任何交易。','sales'=>'營銷','sale'=>'營銷','Cancel Subscription'=>'取消訂閱','The subscription could not be canceled. Please try again later.'=>'無法取消訂閱，請稍後再試。','Canceled'=>'已取消','Warning! This subscription will be canceled. This cannot be undone. \'OK\' to cancel subscription, \'Cancel\' to stop'=>'警告！你將取消此訂閱。此操作無法復原。按「確定」繼續，或按「取消」中止操作。 ','Payment Method'=>'付款方式','regarding a payment methodAny'=>'任何','Select how you would like the sales data to be displayed.'=>'選擇如何顯示銷售數據。','View'=>'查看','Monthly'=>'每月','Weekly'=>'每週','Daily'=>'每日','Dec'=>'十二月','Nov'=>'十一月','Oct'=>'十月','Sep'=>'九月','Aug'=>'八月','Jul'=>'七月','Jun'=>'六月','Apr'=>'四月','Mar'=>'三月','Feb'=>'二月','Jan'=>'一月','Week'=>'週','Refunds'=>'退款','Recurring Payments'=>'訂閱式收費','Subscriptions'=>'訂閱','Orders'=>'訂單','Revenue'=>'收入','There aren\'t any transactions that match your criteria.'=>'沒有符合條件的交易。','orders'=>'張訂單','subscriptions'=>'位訂閱者','Last 30 Days'=>'最近 30 天','Yesterday'=>'昨天','Today'=>'今天','metabox titleFilter'=>'篩選','toolbar labelSales'=>'銷售報告','Select a product field'=>'選擇商品欄位','year(s)'=>'年','month(s)'=>'月','week(s)'=>'週','day(s)'=>'日','Sample Option'=>'樣本選項','Enter an amount'=>'輸入金額','Enabled'=>'已啟用','When conditions are enabled, form submissions will only be sent to the payment gateway when the conditions are met. When disabled, all form submissions will be sent to the payment gateway.'=>'啟用條件邏輯時，填寫的資料只會在符合要求的情況下發送到交易服務供應商。停用時，不論情況都會將資料發送到交易服務供應商。','Conditional Logic'=>'條件邏輯','Options'=>'選項','Map your Form Fields to the available listed fields.'=>'請將表格欄位與相應的資料配對。','Billing Information'=>'帳單資料','Other Settings'=>'其他設定','Select which field determines the payment amount, or select \'Form Total\' to use the total of all pricing fields as the payment amount.'=>'選擇用作交易金額的欄位。你可選擇「表格總額」，將所有商貿欄位的加總作為要收取的交易金額。','Payment Amount'=>'交易金額','Products &amp; Services Settings'=>'商品及服務設定','Enable a trial period.  The user\'s recurring payment will not begin until after this trial period.'=>'啟用試用期功能。在試用期期間，系統不會向用戶收費。','Trial Period'=>'試用期','Trial'=>'試用','Setup Fee'=>'安裝費','Select how many times the recurring payment should be made.  The default is to bill the customer until the subscription is canceled.'=>'選擇系統應向用戶收取多少次費用。預設為一直向用戶收費，直至取消訂閱為止。','infinite'=>'無限','Recurring Times'=>'重複次數','Select your billing cycle.  This determines how often the recurring payment should occur.'=>'選擇結算週期，以決定每隔多久向用戶收費。','Billing Cycle'=>'結算週期','Select which field determines the recurring payment amount, or select \'Form Total\' to use the total of all pricing fields as the recurring amount.'=>'選擇用作訂閱金額的欄位。你可選擇「表格總額」，將所有商貿欄位的加總作為要收取的訂閱金額。','Recurring Amount'=>'訂閱金額','Subscription Settings'=>'訂閱設定','Select a transaction type.'=>'選擇交易類型。','Select a transaction type'=>'選擇交易類型','Enter a feed name to uniquely identify this setup.'=>'輸入訊息流名稱以資識別。','You must add a Credit Card field to your form before creating a feed. Let\'s go %sadd one%s!'=>'在新增訊息流前，你必須先在表格中添加信用卡欄位。立即%s新增信用卡欄位%s！','Form Total'=>'表格總額','Unsupported transaction type'=>'不支援的交易類型','Donations'=>'捐款','Products and Services'=>'商品及服務','Subscription'=>'訂閱式收費','Amount'=>'金額','Transaction Type'=>'交易類型','Subscription has expired. Subscriber Id: %s'=>'訂閱已過期。訂閱者 ID：%s','Subscription has been cancelle